basicgraphics

Class Sprite

  • java.lang.Object
    • basicgraphics.Sprite

  • public class Sprite
extends java.lang.Object
    This class implements an animated object that moves across the screen. It needs a picture, a position, and a velocity. One can override it to tell it how to react to collisions.
